==English==

===Noun===
'''retail'''  {{uncountable}}

# The [[sale]] of [[goods]] [[directly]] to the [[consumer]].

===Adjective===
'''retail'''  (''no'' {{compar}} ''or'' {{superl}})

# Of, or relating to the sale of goods directly to the customer

===Adverb===
'''retail'''

# In retail [[quantities]], or at retail [[price]]s

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|retail||}}  (''transitive'' and ''intransitive'')

# To [[sell]] at retail, or in small quantities directly to customers.

